# File Structure
app.js ------------ main program, handle console and file inputs loop
tr_cmd.js --------- an abstract commands middleware for mapping handlers and parsing commmands
tr_robot.js ------- robot movement logic module

# install
go into src folder and run:
$npm install

# Usage
There are 3 options for running code
$npm start              --- based on console input
$node app.js            --- based on console input
or
$node app.js [filename] --- based on file input

# Test cases
Please run
$mocha tests/*.js
or
$npm test
These test cases cover function of tr_cmd.js and tr_robot.js.

# File input sample
Please see sample.txt, you can modify and run it by:
$node app.js sample.txt
